textBox.richText: Started the day with some warmup-runs with Bhavna, Simon, Lucille, Mark, Rick, and others. Then went to the Outback, met up with PJ, and did some bumps with him and Mark and Rick. After a couple runs there, Mark and Rick split off, and PJ and I played in the Black Forest area. Pretty cool back there...similar to Eagle Wind. Met up with Bijan, and did some other laps there. Started to get tired, met up with Bhavna and crew for some more cruiser runs (and one mini-bump run). Back to the bus, and a typical ride home.
